headline: Zimmer Biomet to Present at the Annual Morgan Stanley Healthcare Conference
summary: Zimmer Biomet Holdings, Inc. (NYSE and SIX: ZBH) today announced that members of the Zimmer Biomet management team will be presenting at the Annual Morgan Stanley Healthcare Conference on Monday, September 8, 2025, at 8:30 a.m. ET.
